column1: Race
Human
Originating from Ashran ; this disloyal inscriptionist wishes to profit from their origins.
Their long hair fall upon their a royal green maid outfit which was passed down from their parents. It seems to have a weird effect on  their gigantic ears.
Race
Human
Her family gave birth to her in Storm Peaks ; this charismatic enchanter strives to profit from their future.
Their inhuman looking body is covered by a handmade orange pair of shoulderpads that  does not suit their beautiful toes.
Race
Blood Elf
Her family gave birth to her in Molten Front ; this unkind inscriptionist expects to unearth their future.
Their apparel consists of a cloth green maid outfit that bears a crest. It perfectly contrasts their absurdly large mouth.
Race
Blood Elf
Their family gave birth to them in Un'goro Crater ; this relentless miner expects to vanquish their destiny.
Their body is covered by a mail white legplate which bears a crest. It perfectly fits their abnormaly large nosedrills.
Race
Human
Originating from Eastern Plaguelands ; this determined Human desires to profit from their destiny.
Their long hair fall upon their a plate blue outfit that  outshines their tiny mouth.
